com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.connector

Interface IExternalDataItemEditor


  • public interface IExternalDataItemEditor
    A mechanism for editing the contents of Items that have been retrieved from an external data source, before they are returned to a client.
    Since:
    3.0

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void edit(Item item, Collection<PropertyBag> propertyBags)
      Modifies the specified Item by adding information that was not present in the external data provider, such as timestamps and grades.

    • Method Detail

      • edit

        void edit(Item item,
          Collection<PropertyBag> propertyBags)
        Modifies the specified Item by adding information that was not present in the external data provider, such as timestamps and grades.
        Parameters:
        item - The Item to be modified.
        propertyBags - PropertyBags that contain information that is associated with this Item.
